cast.overview: Frank, a single man raising his child prodigy niece Mary, is drawn into a custody battle with his mother.
cast.title: Gifted

details.biography: Candace B. Harris is a dedicated and talented film and television actress. She has appeared in supporting roles in films such as Alvin & the Chipmunks: Road Chip (2015), Allegiant: Part 1 (Divergent Series), and Gifted (2017). Harris has also appeared in episodes of Atlanta, Constantine, and Notorious. She is known for her work on Coins for Love, Bobbi Kristina, and Coins Forever.
details.name: Candace B. Harris
